Package: glyexp
Title: Glycoproteomics and Glycomics Experiments
Version: 0.15.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: Provides a tidy data framework for managing glycoproteomics and
    glycomics experimental data. The 'GlycomicSE' and 'GlycoproteomicSE'
    classes extend 'SummarizedExperiment' with validated glycomics and
    glycoproteomics schemas. The package provides dplyr-style data manipulation
    functions (filter, mutate, select, arrange, slice, join) for seamless data
    wrangling and retains the legacy 'experiment()' container temporarily for
    compatibility. As the data core of the 'glycoverse' ecosystem, it provides
    consistent interfaces for data exchange and analysis workflows.
